Package hu.bme.mit.theta.ltl.dsl.gen

Class LTLGrammarBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.ltl.dsl.gen.LTLGrammarBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
LTLGrammarListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class LTLGrammarBaseListener extends Object implements LTLGrammarListener
This class provides an empty implementation of LTLGrammarListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
